<sect1 id="ResolveHostName">
  <title><emphasis role="bold">ResolveHostName</emphasis></title>

  <para><emphasis>result</emphasis> <emphasis role="bold"> :=
  STD.System.Util.ResolveHostName<indexterm>
      <primary>STD.System.Util.ResolveHostName</primary>
    </indexterm> <indexterm>
      <primary>System.Util.ResolveHostName</primary>
    </indexterm> <indexterm>
      <primary>Util.ResolveHostName</primary>
    </indexterm> <indexterm>
      <primary>ResolveHostName</primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis> <emphasis> host </emphasis> <emphasis
  role="bold">);</emphasis></para>

  <informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <colspec colwidth="80.50pt"/>

      <colspec/>

      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry><emphasis>host</emphasis></entry>

          <entry>Uma string terminada por nulo que contém o nome DNS da
          máquina remota.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>Return:<emphasis> </emphasis></entry>

          <entry>ResolveHostName retorna um valor VARSTRING (terminado por
          nulo).</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>

  <para>A função <emphasis role="bold">ResolveHostName </emphasis> executa uma
  busca de DNS para retornar o endereço IP do nome de <emphasis>host
  </emphasis> especificado.</para>

  <para>Exemplo:</para>

  <programlisting format="linespecific">host := 'dataland_dali.br.seisint.com';
OUTPUT(STD.System.Util.ResolveHostName(host));
</programlisting>
</sect1>
